No offence to this song or Ustad Ghulam Mustafa Khan or Coke Studio, In fact, I love this song.
But as per the supreme court ruling. Padma Awards are not titles and their use as a title in the name can result in the fortification of the award. Please drop Padmabhushan from the title of the song. You are abusing the Fundamental right under article 18 of Indian constitution which abolished use of titles.
